msgid "I think I'll just do it later."
msgstr "之後再做吧。"

msgid "That was easy."
msgstr "還真簡單。"

msgid "This isn't the right classroom for that."
msgstr "不是在這間教室。"

msgid "The path is already drawn."
msgstr "路徑已經畫好了。"

msgid "Not yet. I'd rather make sure I have everything I need first."
msgstr "還沒。我要先確定我有所有必要的東西。"

msgid "Not yet. I want to finish preparing the classrooms first."
msgstr "還沒。我要先把教室準備好。"

msgid "There's some chalk here."
msgstr "這裡有一些粉筆。"

msgid "Take it?"
msgstr "拿走嗎？"

msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "I'd rather not get into anymore trouble than I already am."
msgstr "我不想再惹上更多麻煩。"

msgid "This is my desk. I keep all kinds of cool stuff here."
msgstr "這是我的桌子。我把各種酷玩意兒放在這裡。"

msgid "This might be useful."
msgstr "這應該會有用處。"

msgid "Take Dusty Hairpin?"
msgstr "拿走髒兮兮的髮夾？"

msgid "There's nothing else of use for today."
msgstr "這裡已經沒有其他有用處的東西了。"

msgid "My desk. I don't need anything from it right now."
msgstr "我的桌子。我現在不需要從這裡拿東西了。"

msgid "Burning the school down is not part of the ritual."
msgstr "把學校燒掉不是儀式的一部分。"

msgid "There's a pair of scissors here."
msgstr "這裡有一把剪刀。"

msgid "Take Scissors?"
msgstr "拿走剪刀？"

msgid "It's already done."
msgstr "已經完成了。"

msgid "This isn't the time for that."
msgstr "現在不是時候。"

msgid "Return scissors?"
msgstr "放回剪刀？"

msgid "Some geometry books."
msgstr "幾何學課本。"

msgid "A clean chalkboard."
msgstr "乾淨的黑板。"

msgid "A wooden desk."
msgstr "木桌。"

msgid "A paper slip with rules for students."
msgstr "印著校規的紙張。"

msgid "There's no time for rules right now."
msgstr "現在沒時間看校規。"

msgid "Some classroom attendance sheets and schedules."
msgstr "出席表和課表。"

msgid "A happy green plant."
msgstr "快樂的綠色植物。"

msgid "The plant is no longer happy."
msgstr "植物不再快樂了。"

msgid "The teacher's podium."
msgstr "教師的講台。"

msgid "Some boring textbooks."
msgstr "無聊的課本。"

msgid "Some very thick, school-related books."
msgstr "非常厚重、跟學校有關的書本。"

msgid "Some books and... chalk."
msgstr "書本和...粉筆。"

msgid "There's nothing else of use."
msgstr "沒有什麼有用的東西了。"

msgid "A simple trash can. Its contents look trashy."
msgstr "垃圾桶。它的內容物很垃圾。"

msgid "The curtains should stay closed."
msgstr "窗簾應該關上。"

msgid "Should I sort the desks in this classroom now?"
msgstr "我應該現在把教室的桌子排好嗎？"

msgid "Not yet"
msgstr "再等等"

msgid "This should be easy."
msgstr "應該會很簡單。"
